@OmgItsShane wrote:

[quote=“Uncalled, post:53, topic:399146”]Sorry everyone, this project will no longer continue due to me having to cease Vain’s access to the source after deleting my source files and changing the password to the VPS I’ve been paying for, then deleting all the files on the website because he raged because of one of my moderators. I hope you all won’t be disappointed, sorry. I’m pretty upset about this; never expected Vain to act this way, very surprising, very disappointing. Again, I’m very sorry about this everyone. This will be the last time I team up with anyone in MoparScape to work on a project together; I’m tired of being fucked over, I thought that this would be okay seeing how close I was to Vain and assumed he wouldn’t do anything to harm this project. I obviously was wrong.

So please don’t ask me to help you on a project; I’m never going to pair up with anyone on MoparScape; from now on, all my projects are going to be solo. I had paired up with previous people on here in the past and would always end up getting screwed over. So please, never ask me to team with you on your projects, I refuse to get fucked over like I continually have in the past and seem to still continue to do. Vain of all the people on MoparScape, the person I was the closest to on this website has completely crushed all my trust in everyone on MoparScape. One little mishaps like what happened he rages, changes the password to my VPS and deletes the source files, he was very immature about this situation; I can understand him simply leaving the project completely, saying something like “Sorry, I just can’t stand your staff you have and refuse to work with such pricks.” Something like that, but no; he decides to delete the source, change the VPS password, claim that he can do anything he wants because he’s the “owner” and raises Hell on my server abusing my staff verbally, demoting me, saying shit like “Selling Matt’s VPS” through the ::yell command, just being ridiculous, can’t stand that. Please note I am the main owner of this server. I just can no longer work with anyone on this site. I am getting my VPS back, just need to wait about an hour or so before I have the password changed.

Again, I’m very sorry that this all happened.[/quote]

@OP This is a great server you gonna release the better version? ;D
